msgid ""
"Amazon require certain information for the shipping location. Please make "
"sure the following information are set on '%(location_name)s' (%"
"(location)s): street, country and country code."
msgstr ""
"Amazon vyžaduje určité informácie o mieste dodania. Uistite sa, že "
"nasledujúce informácie sú na „%(location_name)s“ (%(location)s) nastavené: "
"ulica, krajina a kód krajiny."

#. module: sale_amazon
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale_amazon/models/stock_picking.py:0
msgid ""
"Amazon requires that a tracking reference is provided with each delivery. "
"Since the current carrier doesn't automatically provide a tracking "
"reference, you need to set one manually."
msgstr ""
"Amazon vyžaduje, aby bolo pri každej dodávke uvedené sledovacie číslo. Keďže "
"súčasný prepravca automaticky neposkytuje sledovacie číslo, je potrebné ho "
"nastaviť ručne."

#. module: sale_amazon
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale_amazon/models/stock_picking.py:0
